data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Boiling Springs! This exquisite traditional residence boasts 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a large bonus room including a master suite on the main floor for the utmost convenience and luxury. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of a meticulously maintained interior. The upgraded kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring modern appliances, quartz countertops, and ample storage space. Whether you're hosting a casual family breakfast or a grand dinner party, the formal dining room is the perfect setting, creating an ambiance of sophistication and charm. The master suite on the main floor provides a peaceful retreat, complete with a private sitting room that can be transformed into your personal oasis. The attached master bathroom offers a spa-like experience with its upgraded fixtures and finishes, ensuring relaxation at the end of a long day. With four additional bedrooms and a bonus room upstairs, there's plenty of space for a growing family or guests. Each room is thoughtfully designed to provide comfort and style, creating a welcoming atmosphere throughout the entire home. One of the highlights of this property is the large wooded lot that spans over .65 of an acre. Imagine enjoying your morning coffee on the back patio, surrounded by the tranquility of nature. The lush greenery provides a serene backdrop, creating a sense of privacy and seclusion. Conveniently located in Boiling Springs, this home offers the perfect blend of suburban tranquility and accessibility to amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful traditional home yours — where timeless elegance meets modern comfort on a private wooded lot.  This home is barely 3 years old and has over 40k worth of builder upgrades! Schedule your viewing today and experience the magic of this exceptional property!
